Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: What sort of pain? If you need to vent this sub is a great place to work through your feelings. Maybe if you can put words to what’s dragging you down you can find a small place to start working on?   If screaming into the void isn’t your thing I get that too! We are all different. Just know that I/ we empathize, you aren’t alone in feeling lost, you aren’t alone in this struggle. I’m not much for prayers but sending good vibes your way.
